---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Annuities - PCFG Insurance Services" description="Secure your retirement with annuities from PCFG Insurance Services. Fixed, variable, and indexed annuities to help grow and protect your retirement savings. Get your free quote today." ogImage="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6801648/pexels-photo-6801648.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200&h=630" ogType="article">
  <Header />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-navy-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Annuities for Retirement Security</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
            Secure your financial future with annuities designed to provide guaranteed income, tax-deferred growth, and peace of mind in retirement. Explore fixed, variable, and indexed annuity options.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="https://pcfginsurance.annuitiesgenius.com/quotes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold text-center transition-colors duration-200">
              Get Annuity Quote
            </a>
            <a href="https://pcfginsurance.annuitiesgenius.com/rates" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="border-2 border-navy-600 text-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-600 hover:text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold text-center transition-colors duration-200">
              View Current Rates
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Free Report and Action Buttons -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Free Retirement Report</h3>
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Top 3 Retirement Mistakes</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
              Download our free report revealing the most common retirement planning mistakes made by people with $250k+ in assets.
            </p>
            <a href="https://pcfginsurance.annuitiesgenius.com/top-3-retirement-mistakes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 inline-block mb-6">
              Download Free Report
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <a href="https://pcfginsurance.annuitiesgenius.com/quotes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full bg-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 block text-center">
              Get Personalized Annuity Quote
            </a>
            <a href="https://pcfginsurance.annuitiesgenius.com/rates" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full border-2 border-navy-600 text-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-600 hover:text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 block text-center">
              View Current Annuity Rates
            </a>
            <a href="tel:877-717-7234" class="w-full border-2 border-gray-300 text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 block text-center">
              Call (877) 717-7234
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- What are Annuities -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What are Annuities?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Annuities are financial products designed to provide a steady stream of income during retirement. They offer tax-deferred growth and can provide guaranteed income for life, making them an essential component of retirement planning.
          </p>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Key Benefits:</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Guaranteed income for life (with certain products)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Tax-deferred growth potential
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Protection from market volatility (fixed annuities)
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                No contribution limits like 401(k)s or IRAs
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Death benefit protection for beneficiaries
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <a href="#quote-form" class="bg-navy-600 hover:bg-navy-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200">
            Get Annuity Quote
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-lg">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">How Annuities Work</h4>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded border-l-4 border-navy-600">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Accumulation Phase</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">You make premium payments that grow tax-deferred over time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded border-l-4 border-navy-600">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Annuitization Phase</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Convert your accumulated value into regular income payments</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded border-l-4 border-navy-600">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Income Phase</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Receive guaranteed payments for a specified period or for life</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Types of Annuities -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Types of Annuities</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Choose the right annuity type based on your risk tolerance, income needs, and retirement timeline.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Fixed Annuities -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Fixed Annuities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Guaranteed interest rate and predictable growth. Perfect for conservative investors who want stability and guaranteed returns.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Features:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Guaranteed minimum interest rate</li>
              <li>• Principal protection</li>
              <li>• Predictable income payments</li>
              <li>• No market risk</li>
              <li>• Tax-deferred growth</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Best For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Conservative investors</li>
              <li>• Those seeking guaranteed returns</li>
              <li>• Risk-averse retirees</li>
              <li>• Stable income planning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <a href="#quote-form" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 w-full block text-center">
            Learn About Fixed Annuities
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Variable Annuities -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Variable Annuities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Investment options with potential for higher returns. Your account value fluctuates based on the performance of underlying investments.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Features:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Investment sub-account options</li>
              <li>• Potential for higher returns</li>
              <li>• Professional money management</li>
              <li>• Death benefit guarantees</li>
              <li>• Optional living benefit riders</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Best For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Growth-oriented investors</li>
              <li>• Those comfortable with market risk</li>
              <li>• Long-term retirement planning</li>
              <li>• Seeking inflation protection</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <a href="#quote-form" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 w-full block text-center">
            Learn About Variable Annuities
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Indexed Annuities -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Indexed Annuities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Growth potential linked to market index performance with principal protection. Combines the safety of fixed annuities with growth potential.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Features:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Principal protection guarantee</li>
              <li>• Growth linked to market indices</li>
              <li>• Participation rates and caps</li>
              <li>• No direct market investment</li>
              <li>• Minimum guaranteed returns</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Best For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Moderate risk tolerance</li>
              <li>• Seeking growth with protection</li>
              <li>• Long-term accumulation</li>
              <li>• Balanced approach to retirement</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <a href="#quote-form" class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 w-full block text-center">
            Learn About Indexed Annuities
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Immediate vs Deferred -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Immediate vs. Deferred Annuities</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Choose when you want to start receiving income payments based on your retirement timeline and current needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        
        <!-- Immediate Annuities -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Immediate Annuities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Start receiving income payments immediately (within 12 months) after making your premium payment. Perfect for those already in retirement.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Key Features:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Income starts within 12 months
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Guaranteed lifetime income options
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Single premium payment
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                No accumulation phase
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Ideal For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Current retirees needing income now</li>
              <li>• Those with lump sum to invest</li>
              <li>• Replacing pension income</li>
              <li>• Immediate income needs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Deferred Annuities -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3a4 4 0 118 0v4m-4 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zm6 0a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Deferred Annuities</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Accumulate value over time before starting income payments. Ideal for those still working and planning for future retirement income.
          </p>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Key Features:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Tax-deferred accumulation phase
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Flexible premium payments
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Choose when to start income
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                Longer growth potential
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Ideal For:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Pre-retirees still working</li>
              <li>• Long-term retirement planning</li>
              <li>• Building retirement income</li>
              <li>• Tax-deferred growth seekers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Annuity Benefits -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Consider Annuities for Retirement?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Annuities offer unique benefits that can complement your overall retirement strategy and provide financial security.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Guaranteed Income -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Guaranteed Income</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Create a personal pension with guaranteed income payments that can last for life, providing security in retirement.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Tax Advantages -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-navy-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Tax-Deferred Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Your money grows tax-deferred, meaning you don't pay taxes on gains until you withdraw, potentially allowing for faster accumulation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- No Contribution Limits -->
        <div class="text-center">
